{
  "stem": "2004.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was operated by medical students, at best-- Jewish medical students that never-- that never-- that had never had a chance to become doctors.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they had a basic knowledge of what to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had a lot of home remedies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Believe it or not, we learned-- I learned that if I have an infection, the way to cure an infection-- we didn't-- in those days, the big item, as I later found out, was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was a sort of a salve, called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now [NON-ENGLISH] is you have an infection and you want it to come to head.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You put that [NON-ENGLISH] on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that brought it to it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now, we didn't have any of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But we had home remedies.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We used to take a piece of potato, raw potato, slice it, put it on your wound.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it did miracles for you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It did the same thing that that [NON-ENGLISH] did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "A slice of potato cured-- cured certain things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So we learned to-- how to do home remedies.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "To a great extent, they worked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in any event, I was-- my detail was-- I was in charge-- not only in charge, but I was doing the actual work.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was only one doing the work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had to build up the pressure in that-- in that large kettle, outdoor kettle.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had to make sure that the pressure was there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had to load up the clothing, do the cleaning, take it out, put it in a designated spot, put in more cleaning.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now my work was at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now my lucky break was that this kettle, that-- that sanitizing kettle, was located near the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at night, the Germans, didn't-- they didn't watch us that closely.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
